# How to view and configure server health reports in Plesk


There are five sections indicating the health of the different types of system resources. Services, Disk, Memory, CPU, and Network.

In order to view the health of system resources, first login to your Plesk administrative panel as admin and do the following steps:

1) Select **Health Monitoring** from the **Home** page and expand the sections.
